  "detailed_description": "Neocon Tower Defense 3 is a finger-blisteringly action-packed, fast-paced tower defense game that progressively intensifies with each level.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhile the initial stages serve as a gentle introduction to the game mechanics, later levels become increasingly challenging, inundating you with enemy forces from all directions. You'll need split-second decisions to figure out how to counter the relentless and nameless enemy hordes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith a selection of 20 towers and 10 add-ons and 24 perks to choose from, there's always a new strategy to try out against the escalating threat.",
